mation.com/abonnement-newsletter-wpf/">Abonnez-vous &agrave; la newsletter</a> !<br></p>\n<hr>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:2:{s:4:"date";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2016-07-08T10:00:50+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"WPFormation";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2196:"<div>\n<p><img width="1200" height="682" src="https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo.jpg" class="attachment-Large size-Large wp-post-image" alt="jetpack-logo" style="display: block; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; max-width: 640px; max-height: 400px; " srcset="https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo.jpg 1200w, https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo-300x171.jpg 300w, https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo-768x436.jpg 768w, https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo-1024x582.jpg 1024w, https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo-600x341.jpg 600w, https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo-610x347.jpg 610w, https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo-810x460.jpg 810w, https://wpf-1278.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/0201/07/jetpack-logo-1140x648.jpg 1140w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px">Jetpack est un super mega plugin qui connecte et&nbsp;ajoute de nombreuses fonctionnalit&eacute;s &agrave; votre site WordPress&nbsp;auto-h&eacute;berg&eacute; via la plateforme WordPress.com. Avec son million d&rsquo;installations actives, Jetpack reste l''une des principales r&eacute