(33, 1, '2016-02-12 16:21:48', '2016-02-12 15:21:48', 'Let me introduced myself. I''m Julie, 19 currently in 2nd year of BTS Assistant manager. I live in Illzach in Upper Rhine (68) and I''m <strong>pumped</strong>.\r\nVery interested in photography since youngest it''s only at 19 I decided to start as an <strong>amateur photographer</strong>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI wish you a good visit and <strong>do not hesitate to contact</strong> me for more informations or expose me your projects.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ornare faucibus tincidunt. Vestibulum elementum finibus accumsan. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Morbi egestas est lorem, id bibendum ipsum molestie a. Fusce et dignissim sapien. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Cras faucibus, lacus at sagittis faucibus, ipsum libero sagittis felis, vitae hendrerit metus felis eget dui. Nullam ultrices et tellus id feugiat. Curabitur lobortis ut lacus a dignissim. Nunc condimentum odio et sapien condimentum, quis efficitur ante accumsan. Quisque non quam vitae neque elementum euismod sed eget eros. Nunc id dolor velit. Nulla suscipit ullamcorper quam, et semper magna euismod et. Donec ultrices rhoncus posuere.', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'aboutme', '', '', '2016-09-07 13:28:42', '2016-09-07 12:28:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=33', 1, 'page', '', 0),
